    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your Inventory</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every decision about which item to put in your backpack and exactly how it synergizes with the rest can be crucial. Your survival depends on your ability to balance risk and reward by strategically planning your actions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/b67cee3d04e22cc168759f8952e69738.poster.avif?t=1733154195\" width=506 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/b67cee3d04e22cc168759f8952e69738.webm?t=1733154195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/b67cee3d04e22cc168759f8952e69738.mp4?t=1733154195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique backpack system that allows the player to collect and combine items to create powerful sets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic bullet hell gameplay that will dilute thoughtful backpacking sessions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You create your own build that interests you the most</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hundreds of items with their own features and use conditions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bosses, each with unique mechanics and features</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/32ef19e2e9307fc82003434dc697b47f.poster.avif?t=1733154195\" width=506 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/32ef19e2e9307fc82003434dc697b47f.webm?t=1733154195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/32ef19e2e9307fc82003434dc697b47f.mp4?t=1733154195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft/Builds</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy from the merchant and combine different weapons/clothing/amulets and expand your backpack to incredible sizes. Create a class that you like: start as a warrior with great stamina or rebuild into a life-stealing mage, or maybe you like to develop through creature summoning or marksmanship? Your choice is limited only by your skill and luck!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/4a129cb55982f188671c01aaa39178c5.poster.avif?t=1733154195\" width=506 height=506 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/4a129cb55982f188671c01aaa39178c5.webm?t=1733154195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215500/extras/4a129cb55982f188671c01aaa39178c5.mp4?t=1733154195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare for a challenge where every battle is a dance on the edge of survival, and every new item could be the key to victory or doom!</p>",
